## Architecture Overview

The hook system follows a multi-tier architecture that organizes hooks by execution phase and concern. The system initializes hooks across five primary tiers: Session (24), Tool-Guard (15), Transform (7), Continuation (7), and Skill (2). Additionally, Team Mode introduces specific event handlers for member coordination.

