## Disabling Hooks

Hooks can be globally disabled via the `disabled_hooks` array in the configuration file (`oh-my-opencode.jsonc`). The system uses `safeCreateHook` to isolate initialization, ensuring that a failing hook does not prevent the entire plugin from loading [src/plugin/hooks/create-session-hooks.ts80-81](https://github.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-openagent/blob/9edaa6e9/src/plugin/hooks/create-session-hooks.ts#L80-L81)

